02:15:28,658 --> 02:15:30,784
Is this guy bothering you?

1250
02:15:31,995 --> 02:15:33,036
Mother!

1251
02:15:34,580 --> 02:15:38,458
Go away. This is a very sacred moment.

1252
02:18:48,316 --> 02:18:50,275
He's got away from us, Jack.

1253
02:18:50,359 --> 02:18:53,653
I'm afraid you're right, Mr. Helpmann.
He's gone.

1254
02:19:35,112 --> 02:19:38,657
<i>Tomorrow was another day</i>

1255
02:19:40,117 --> 02:19:44,037
<i>The morning found me miles away</i>

1256
02:19:45,331 --> 02:19:49,626
<i>With still a million things to say</i>

1257
02:19:53,130 --> 02:19:55,382
<i>Now</i>

1258
02:19:56,092 --> 02:20:00,387
<i>As twilight beams the sky above</i>

1259
02:20:01,430 --> 02:20:04,849
<i>Recalling thrills of our love</i>

1260
02:20:06,894 --> 02:20:10,897
<i>There's one thing I'm certain of</i>

1261
02:20:11,649 --> 02:20:16,403
<i>Return I will</i>

1262
02:20:18,239 --> 02:20:24,244
<i>To old Brazil</i>